title: Munsterhaus
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, International, Organic, Western, Buffet, Fast food, Salad bar, Take-out
description: A cafeteria that features a large buffet of hot and cold dishes, from which you can take what you please (small, medium, or large plates). The take-out option is one (large) size only. Similar to The Tofu Shop in Richmond but large and a cafe feel. Has Wi-Fi and a toy corner for children.
